---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cols">
      <div>
        <div class="brand">로직크래프트 <span>LogicCraft</span></div>
        <p class="claim">생각하는 힘을 키우는 앱을 만듭니다.</p>
      </div>
      <nav class="links" aria-label="푸터 메뉴">
        <a href="/apps">앱</a>
        <a href="/about">소개</a>
        <a href="/contact">문의</a>
        <a href="mailto:smartsikhye@gmail.com">smartsikhye@gmail.com</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="biz">
      대표자 최우식 · 사업자등록번호 302-11-03141
    </div>
    <div class="copy">© {year} LogicCraft. All rights reserved.</div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    padding: 3rem 0 2.5rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
  }
  .cols {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
  }
  .brand { font-weight: 800; color: var(--ink); font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .brand span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-left: 0.3rem; }
  .claim { margin: 0.4rem 0 0; color: var(--sub); }
  .links { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.1rem; align-items: center; }
  .links a { color: var(--sub); font-weight: 600; }
  .biz { line-height: 1.8; }
  .copy { margin-top: 0.4rem; }
</style>
